
# Deployment

Use Fabric to deploy a new OpenResty web server onto an Ubuntu 16.04
server after completing the following new server guides:

- https://www.linode.com/docs/getting-started
- https://www.linode.com/docs/security/securing-your-server

Add new environments into the STAGES dict in fabfile.py.

On a fresh Ubuntu server the following should get the we bserver up
and running:

- `fab {{your_env}} install`
